\par \tab As the honourable Orders of the Empire go, the Order of the High Helms is the \tab newly conceived baby. On the 1st Sigmarzeit 2511 Emperor Karl-Franz I hit upon an \tab 
idea that struck his fancy; the creation of an Order of very tall and very tough knights \tab (with the emphasis on tall).
\par \tab Boredom can do incredible things...
\par \tab One month later the Order was constituted and recruitment began.
\par \tab Unsurprisingly the Order has been fairly slow to grow in numbers due to its strict \tab (read: ridiculous) entry requirements. 
\par 
\par {\b\i\f32 Base of Operations -} 
\par \tab At present they are being drilled in Altdorf, and consist of 24 fully trained knights
\par \tab with a further 12 in training.
